10. Conclusion
The Advanced Student Performance Management System demonstrates how Java OOP concepts, JDBC, and SQL Server can be effectively integrated to build a comprehensive academic management solution.
The system simplifies student performance tracking, improves data accuracy, and provides reliable academic reporting for both students and faculty members.
Its modular and scalable design allows for easy extension and future upgrades, making it suitable for real-world academic environments.
